OL,3,CReform-run council passes first budget
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of 'extreme risk'
OL,6,FReform UK's "flagship" local authority
OL,7,Fin Kent has passed its first budget
OL,8,Fdespite warnings from opposition
OL,9,Fleaders of "extreme risk" and it being
OL,10,F"potentially reckless".
OL,12,FKent County Council's deputy leader
OL,13,FBrian Collins summed up the budget as
OL,14,Fbeing "carefully thought through"
OL,15,Fadding: "Some people call it risky, I
OL,16,Fcall it bold".
OL,18,FCouncil leader Linden Kemkaran
OL,19,Fdescribed it as a "sensible, low tax
OL,20,Fbudget".
