OL,3,CReform-run council passes first budget
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of 'extreme risk'
OL,6,FThe vote was carried with 48
OL,7,Fcouncillors in favour, 26 against and
OL,8,Fone abstention in a total of 75 votes
OL,9,Ffrom members present.
OL,11,FReform councillors currently represent
OL,12,F48 out of the 81 seats following their
OL,13,Fvictory at local elections in May last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThere was applause from the Reform
OL,17,Fmembers in the chamber for the result
OL,18,Ffollowing eight hours of debate at the
OL,19,Fcounty hall in Maidstone.
