OL,3,CReform-run council passes first budget
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of 'extreme risk'
OL,6,FOpposition parties had warned against
OL,7,F"dangerously low" reserves and the
OL,8,Fauthority's "highest ever exposure to
OL,9,Ffinancial risk" totalling more than
OL,10,F#410 million on the risk register.
OL,12,FKent's Reform leaders have secured a
OL,13,F3.99% council tax increase, 1% under
OL,14,Fthe limit before a referendum is
OL,15,Frequired, despite promising ahead of
OL,16,Ftheir election win not to raise tax.
