OL,3,CReform-run council passes first budget
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of 'extreme risk'
OL,6,FMs Kemkaran said Reform would prefer
OL,7,Fnot to propose a council tax increase
OL,8,Fat all but given "the dire legacy we
OL,9,Finherited", alongside an unprecedented
OL,10,Frise in demands and costs for services
OL,11,Fsuch as social care, "this is simply
OL,12,Fnot possible".
OL,14,FBut opposition bosses have criticised
OL,15,Fthe move for not raising it to the
OL,16,Fmaximum possible, which will leave the
OL,17,Fcouncil with #10 million less for the
OL,18,Fnext financial year that could have
OL,19,Fprotected services and reserves.
