OL,3,CReform-run council passes first budget
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of 'extreme risk'
OL,6,FLeader of the opposition, Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat Antony Hook, said it is a
OL,8,Fbudget that is "built on broken
OL,9,Fpromises to the taxpayer", and
OL,10,Fdescribed it as a "casino budget"
OL,11,Fwhere Reform have already "lost
OL,12,Fcontrol" this year with a forecast
OL,13,Foverspend of #36.5 million.
OL,15,FHe said: "They are putting our risk
OL,16,Flevels on steroids, while burning the
OL,17,Fsafety net.
OL,19,F"And it gambles the solvency of this
OL,20,Fauthority on the hope that risks rated
OL,21,Fas likely won't materialise."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
