OL,3,CReform-run council passes first budget
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of 'extreme risk'
OL,6,F"It is a budget of failure, and
OL,7,Fextreme risk."
OL,9,FIn Mr Shipton's statement, called
OL,10,FSection 25 assurance, it also said the
OL,11,Flevel of forecast overspend for this
OL,12,Ffinancial year poses a "significant
OL,13,Frisk" to the council's reserves and
OL,14,Ffinancial sustainability.
OL,16,FIt added: "Without improvement there
OL,17,Fis a risk that the general reserve
OL,18,Favailable in 2026-27 would be below
OL,19,Fthe recommended 5% to 10% target
OL,20,Frange."
