OL,6,FThe budget papers said the proposals
OL,7,Fare balanced by #25 million in "one-
OL,8,Foff measures" that will need "to be
OL,9,Freplaced by sustainable solutions in
OL,10,Ffuture years".
OL,12,FMr Hook said the budget selling off
OL,13,Fassets to pay for day-to-day spending
OL,14,F"leaves a financial hole" for the
OL,15,Ffollowing year, warning: "You can only
OL,16,Fsell an asset once."
