OL,3,CReform-run council passes first budget
OL,4,Cdespite warnings of 'extreme risk'
OL,6,FSpeaking against the budget, leader of
OL,7,Fthe independent group, Paul Thomas,
OL,8,Fsaid it was "blind ambition" and
OL,9,F"potentially reckless", adding: "If it
OL,10,Fgoes wrong and you need to dig deeper
OL,11,Finto reserves."
OL,13,FConservative leader Harry Rayner
OL,14,Fdescribed it as a "real gambler's
OL,15,Fbudget" while Labour's chief Alister
OL,16,FBrady said Kent County Council was
OL,17,F"heading for financial danger" under
OL,18,FReform.
OL,20,FBut Ms Kemkaran said: "This is a
OL,21,Fresponsible budget.
