OL,6,FThe risk register rates the current
OL,7,Flikelihood of the risk as four out of
OL,8,Ffive, noting pressures from rising
OL,9,Fdemand, workforce shortages and
OL,10,Finflating costs.
OL,12,FIt said to address the budget gap for
OL,13,F2026-27, there is a limit for price
OL,14,Fuplifts for care providers between 0-
OL,15,F3.6% among the measures, but it notes
OL,16,Fthe move could worsen recruitment and
OL,17,Fretention issues and lead to contract
OL,18,Fhandbacks and more costly placements.
